Everyone here: I think the Magic Budget Template is now ready to use. To use it, start with [the documentation](/t/id/9097) – everything is, or should be, in there. Starting from now, this is the new default how to do a budget (and we need to stick to it to enable company-wide cash flow controlling).  Let me know in this thread what's missing or does not work.

